{'id': 167051667, 'user_id': 2094343778, 'title': '', 'text': '转：1.<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600887?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600887?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">伊利股份</a>，个人第三重仓股，还没有买够股数，有子弹了，40元左右会择机继续加仓。2021年目标价50―65，目前2500亿，明年可以看到3000-4000亿。龙头，高频刚需，渠道下沉能力强（备注，渠道下沉能力强的公牛集团、<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH603899?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH603899?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">晨光文具</a>只要有机会都是可以长期介入），长期对标<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/NSRGY?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/NSRGY?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">雀巢</a>，目标1万亿，真的不是痴人说梦，中国13亿张嘴会支撑起这个价值。<br/>2.<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600009?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600009?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">上海机场</a>，困境反转，受疫情反复影响，前期低位买入又卖出了，未来在疫情稳定情况下，会继续买入，个人感觉70以下买入风险不太大，长期持有优质标的，2021看到100问题不大（机场免税合作伙伴。中国中免已经飞天，如有回调到前期底部180元附近&nbsp;，参与也没啥大问题）。<br/>3.<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ002714?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ002714?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">牧原股份</a>，非瘟影响下高速扩张，逆势飞扬，形成龙头地位，大家担心的明年猪肉价格下滑，牧原会通过养殖技术优势、规模优势和成本优势及新增屠宰增利来进行对冲，可以保证利润的稳定增长，70以下继续买入，长期持有，2021年目标价100-120，不敢说太高，怕被喷，我内心目标应该可以看到5000亿。<br/>4.<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300015?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300015?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">爱尔眼科</a>和<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600763?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600763?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">通策医疗</a>，医疗服务双雄，不收集采影响，商业模式好，走势一致，一路上扬，一直很贵。继续持有，每一次大回调都是买入良机。（眼科还有一个小家伙光正眼科，要重视，高毅在里面不是闹着玩的，可以观察，适量介入。<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300595?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300595?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">欧普康视</a>角膜塑形镜龙头，创了新高，业绩稳定增长，就看有没有上车机会了，目前只能观赏）<br/>5.<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600036?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600036?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">招商银行</a>和<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ002142?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ002142?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">宁波银行</a>，银行股双雄，2020在让利1.5亿大背景下，应该会做比较大的利润调节技术处理，明年业绩会飞上天，坚定看好，招行40以下，宁波31以下应该都是很好的长期介入点位，喜欢稳健的可以参与。<br/>6.<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH601318?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH601318?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">中国平安</a>，大家伙，保险股龙头，机构票。最近公司不是太平，投资汇丰、高管异动带来不确定性，但其龙头地位不改，金融集团+科技金融确定其护城河，大象也能跳舞，近期走势平台稳步上扬，80以下，大资金可以慢慢建仓，长线票，想短期大幅上涨就不要参与了。<br/>7.<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300059?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300059?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">东方财富</a>和<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600030?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600030?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">中信证券</a>，券商双雄，东方财富线上龙头，中信证券传统券商龙头。牛市来了，券商股肯定不会缺席。东方财富25，中信证券24左右都是建仓好机会，长线持有必有厚报。<br/>8.<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600276?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600276?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">恒瑞医药</a>，创新药龙头，在研品种多，2020前抑后扬，目前处于相对高位，本人继续持有，如果市场整体回调，90元上下可以继续增持，长期持有，必有厚报。（2020年受集采及疫情影响，走得比较差的<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300573?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300573?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">兴齐眼药</a>、<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300558?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300558?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">贝达药业</a>、<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600380?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH600380?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">健康元</a>、<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ000513?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ000513?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">丽珠集团</a>、<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH603987?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SH603987?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">康德莱</a>、<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300326?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" title="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ300326?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_source=0105" target="_blank">凯利泰</a>、<a href="https://xueqiu.com/S/SZ002901?from=status_stock_match&amp;xueqiu_status_id=167045713&amp;xueqiu_status_from_source=hotstuff&amp;xueqiu_status_source=statusdetail&amp;xueqiu_private_from_